  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Botomy is a strategy game where players program their bot to compete against others in an online arena. Precision and planning are everything. Decide, in real time, which items are worth collecting or how to battle against different enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game uses a simple client/server architecture to pass game state information to your code. Your code responds with a list of moves to be executed by your character. Edit and execute your code in real-time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the built in editor for Javascript, or spin up your own controller server in any language/framework (typescript and python templates are provided).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game modes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free For All Mode</strong> – Compete in different maps to optimize your bot’s decisions and logic. Highest XP wins the match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival Mode</strong> – Battle against endless waves of enemies. Work together with other players to outsmart, outlast, and out-code.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>NEW</u></i> Training Room</strong> - Set up custom scenarios to test and refine your code. Hone your combat algorithms. Perfect your movement around obstacles. Optimize your collection strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basic Moves:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Attack</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/f2cdd028aaf263c8a1afc27855165c49.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/f2cdd028aaf263c8a1afc27855165c49.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/f2cdd028aaf263c8a1afc27855165c49.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Shield</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/4d2274e14c90b73bbda832c1ae75ed81.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/4d2274e14c90b73bbda832c1ae75ed81.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/4d2274e14c90b73bbda832c1ae75ed81.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Move</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/a6437d6ab6b7e5f73d0367bc0acacf2e.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/a6437d6ab6b7e5f73d0367bc0acacf2e.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/a6437d6ab6b7e5f73d0367bc0acacf2e.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Combine moves</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/d3a0ec86ab5267853f7d208a227feb2a.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/d3a0ec86ab5267853f7d208a227feb2a.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/d3a0ec86ab5267853f7d208a227feb2a.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Items</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Big Potions - Healing</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/46ff1bba4c9e4796b33d85fce7bc2a82.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/46ff1bba4c9e4796b33d85fce7bc2a82.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/46ff1bba4c9e4796b33d85fce7bc2a82.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Rings - Cloaking</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/cb55caf28b7ad1f117e5e0096c184728.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/cb55caf28b7ad1f117e5e0096c184728.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/cb55caf28b7ad1f117e5e0096c184728.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Speed Zappers</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/f2fac4ec23dafd51f7f09e2211ac4ca2.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/f2fac4ec23dafd51f7f09e2211ac4ca2.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/f2fac4ec23dafd51f7f09e2211ac4ca2.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special power ups</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Bomb</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/e281d90928d9ffc009e921178a95e47c.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/e281d90928d9ffc009e921178a95e47c.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/e281d90928d9ffc009e921178a95e47c.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Shockwave</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/b83c05e21f8a534120a2d1e580455513.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/b83c05e21f8a534120a2d1e580455513.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/b83c05e21f8a534120a2d1e580455513.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Freeze</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/6edc98665e90b6d4ccde02140144d34d.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/6edc98665e90b6d4ccde02140144d34d.webm?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/6edc98665e90b6d4ccde02140144d34d.mp4?t=1749588546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Power Ups</strong>– Equip special attacks like <strong>Freeze</strong>, <strong>Bomb</strong>, and <strong>Shockwave</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Kill Streaks</strong> – Your character will <i>overclock</i> <strong>Speed</strong>, <strong>Attack</strong>, and <strong>Health</strong> with each killstreak achieved; culminating in a <strong>Super Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Skill Trees </strong>– Customize your play style by choosing which upgrades to spend your skill points on: Speed, Health, or Attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Global Leaderboards</strong> – Track your progress and rise through the ranks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Practice Offline</strong> – Test your bot before going live</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Choose Your Language</strong> – Program in your preferred coding language or use the built in Javascript editor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re a beginner or a seasoned coder, <strong>Botomy</strong> is a challenging new way to apply your programming skills. The best strategy wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can your bot reach level 30?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dev Environment Info: </strong>The built in language support is javascript but you can spin up your own custom local development environments in any language.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Botomy is a strategy game where players program their bot to compete against others in an online arena. Precision and planning are everything. Decide, in real time, which items are worth collecting or how to battle against different enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game uses a simple client/server architecture to pass game state information to your code. Your code responds with a list of moves to be executed by your character. Edit and execute your code in real-time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the built in editor for Javascript, or spin up your own controller server in any language/framework (typescript and python templates are provided).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game modes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free For All Mode</strong> – Compete in different maps to optimize your bot’s decisions and logic. Highest XP wins the match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival Mode</strong> – Battle against endless waves of enemies. Work together with other players to outsmart, outlast, and out-code.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>NEW</u></i> Training Room</strong> - Set up custom scenarios to test and refine your code. Hone your combat algorithms. Perfect your movement around obstacles. Optimize your collection strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basic Moves:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Attack</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566430/extras/f2cdd028aaf263c8a1afc27855165c49.poster.avif?t=1749588546\" width=380 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app